Class PControlAF

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ControlAF
      • model.PControlAF

  • public class PControlAF
extends ControlAF
    Extends the class Control AF Adding the probability distributions p1, p2, p3 for uncertain arguments, uncertain attacks and undirected attacks p3: ATT -> pd1, pd2
